OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FWhen it rains it pours as the saying
OL,7,Fgoes. At Molineux last night, the
OL,8,Fheavens truly opened on Aston Villa.
OL,10,FLike many football fans, I expected
OL,11,Fthis to be the perfect opportunity for
OL,12,FUnai Emery's men to silence the
OL,13,Fdoubters. Facing a local rival
OL,14,Fdestined for relegation, it should
OL,15,Fhave been a night for a statement
OL,16,FVilla outing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FInstead, football in its twisted and
OL,7,Ffunny way, reminded us that if it was
OL,8,Fplayed on paper - it would be boring.
OL,9,FThe two teams of course looked some
OL,10,Fdistance apart before a ball was
OL,11,Fkicked. But full credit must go to Rob
OL,12,FEdwards' Wolves, who looked the better
OL,13,Fside by a country mile.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FFor the Villa faithful who had made
OL,7,Fthe short trip, it was a harrowing
OL,8,Fwatch. Acting captain Ezri Konsa had
OL,9,Fto be pulled away from travelling
OL,10,Ffans, Jadon Sancho looked furious at
OL,11,Fbeing substituted, only matched by his
OL,12,Fmanager's fury at the lack of added
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,FDespite what many would call a shock
OL,16,Fscoreline, fans told me this was a
OL,17,Fresult that had been coming.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FJust one win in six, and a string of
OL,7,Flethargic displays since the turn of
OL,8,Fthe year suggest that Villa's record
OL,9,Fbreaking 11 match winning streak looks
OL,10,Fa distant memory - despite only being
OL,11,Fweeks ago. In football, things move
OL,12,Ffast don't they.
OL,14,FWhat has happened to Aston Villa?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FWell, maybe nothing yet. As of the
OL,7,Fafternoon of Saturday 28 February,
OL,8,FVilla remarkably remain in third place
OL,9,Fin the Premier League. Of course Villa
OL,10,Flook firmly out of the title race now,
OL,11,Fbut the manager is on the record
OL,12,Fsaying his team are not 'contenders'
OL,13,Fanyway.
OL,15,FThe immediate goal must be a place in
OL,16,Fthe Champions League. But what is the
OL,17,Fprimary culprit of Villa's slump? It
OL,18,Fseems cliched, but it is injuries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FJohn McGinn, Boubacar Kamara and Youri
OL,7,FTielemans - all out. Tielemans and
OL,8,FMcGinn will be hoping to come back
OL,9,Fnext month, but Kamara is out for the
OL,10,Fseason. And without the Frenchman in
OL,11,Fmidfield, Villa really are a worse
OL,12,Fteam.
OL,14,FTheir win rate drops to roughly 16%
OL,15,Fwithout him. Form more akin to a
OL,16,Frelegation scrap, rather than a
OL,17,FChampions League charge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FTheir midfield replacements, Amadou
OL,7,FOnana and Douglas Luiz look well off
OL,8,Fthe mark having both come back from
OL,9,Finjuries earlier this season.
OL,11,FWithout their midfield metronomes who
OL,12,Fkeep things ticking along, Villa often
OL,13,Flook directionless and can't create as
OL,14,Fmany big chances. With just one goal
OL,15,Ffrom open play in their last five
OL,16,Fmatches.
OL,18,FAnother cause for concern is Villa's
OL,19,FPremier League all time top
OL,20,Fgoalscorer, which seems paradoxical
OL,21,Feven to write.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FTammy Abraham rejoined Villa in
OL,7,FJanuary, but he remains stuck behind
OL,8,Fthe favoured Ollie Watkins. Abraham
OL,9,Fjoins a list of Jhon Duran and Donyell
OL,10,FMalen of fan favourite strikes who are
OL,11,Falways benched in Watkins' favour.
OL,13,FDespite a brilliant contribution off
OL,14,Fthe bench at Stamford Bridge, in a
OL,15,Fgame where Villa really should have
OL,16,Flost, Watkins has rarely featured from
OL,17,Fthe bench since - to the frustration
OL,18,Fof many Villa faithful who feel he
OL,19,Fshould be benched in favour of Tammy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FEight goals for a player with the
OL,7,Ftalent to score in big moments for
OL,8,Fclub and country should be cause for
OL,9,Fconcern.
OL,11,FPerhaps it's something more simple -
OL,12,Ffatigue. Perhaps Villa are tired,
OL,13,Fthat's why they look out of ideas in
OL,14,Fan attacking sense. Morgan Rogers,
OL,15,Ftheir star player this season, has
OL,16,Fbarely missed a minute - even in the
OL,17,Fcup competitions where you may expect
OL,18,Fhim to be rested. In his place, no-one
OL,19,Fcan quite fill his boots and what he
OL,20,Foffers for the team.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FThe tiredness across the whole team
OL,7,Fmeans lapses in concentration, and
OL,8,Fdifficulty in breaking down teams who
OL,9,Fsit back and play with unmatched
OL,10,Faggression. To Leeds, Brentford,
OL,11,FEverton and Wolves' credit - they've
OL,12,Fall got the better of Villa in recent
OL,13,Fweeks playing this way.
OL,15,FWhat's next for Villa?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FIn what fans and pundits alike thought
OL,7,Fwould've been a routine January for
OL,8,FVilla, they're now approaching some of
OL,9,Ftheir toughest fixtures this season.
OL,10,FChelsea next week, and a trip to Old
OL,11,FTrafford on the horizon sandwiched in
OL,12,Fbetween a return to Lille.
OL,14,FOf course that fixture required some
OL,15,FEmiliano Martinez penalty antics to
OL,16,Fget over the line in the Conference
OL,17,FLeague two years ago.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FWhile Villa have stumbled, their
OL,7,Frivals have surged. Manchester United
OL,8,Fare back to their best under Michael
OL,9,FCarrick and Chelsea under Liam
OL,10,FRosenoir. The next three fixtures
OL,11,Freally couldn't be more make or break.
OL,13,FAnd as of writing this, Villa could
OL,14,Feven end the weekend in fifth place if
OL,15,FManchester United and Chelsea win
OL,16,Ftheir fixtures.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FFailure to get Champions League for a
OL,7,Fsecond year in a row could be dire for
OL,8,FVilla and have consequences beyonf the
OL,9,Fpitch. With the club reporting losses
OL,10,Fearlier this week of #80 million
OL,11,Fpounds, missing out on European
OL,12,Frevenue might force the sale of prize
OL,13,Fassets like Morgan Rogers - a painful
OL,14,Fecho to the departures of Douglas Luiz
OL,15,Fand Jacob Ramsey, which I speculated
OL,16,Fon two years ago.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772499776
OL,3,CAn insight into Villa's villainous
OL,4,Cform - as top four hopes hit a wall
OL,6,FBut Villa can course correct as early
OL,7,Fas Wednesday. The players will walk
OL,8,Fout to Ozzy Osbourne's Crazy Train as
OL,9,Fthey always do. But as the lyrics go,
OL,10,Fthey might not be 'going off the
OL,11,Frails' just yet - but they certainly
OL,12,Fare rattling over some dangerous track.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
